name: Le Malin (Azur Lane) (All skins)  (9MB update)
description:
Le Malin (Azur Lane) LoRA

12-05-2023/V7 Update:

  • Improve Le Malin Muse accuracy

16-02-2023/V6 Update:

  • Reduce the model file size to 9MB.

  • Use a way lower network dim (8 instead of 160) and Alpha (1 instead of 160) to prevent overfitting

  • More flexible

  • Rebalanced dataset (I uploaded it)

  • Trained on NAI instead of AnythingV3

  • Add a new token for each canon outfit (using booru token was a bad idea):
    LeMalinDefault

    LeMalinLapin

    LeMalinMuse

    LeMalinSundress

    LeMalinSwimsuit

I will probably make a V7 that use noise offset.

I don't recommend using V5 (overfitted)

This is a LoRA, this mean that you need to update Voldy/AUTOMATIC1111's webui to use it (use git pull) .

Recommended Weight:

1.0 unless you want to use multiple LoRAs

For Le Malin Muse: 0.8-1.0 (because of background overfit)

Recommended prompt:

That LoRA can reproduice all her game skin and version (as 12/05/2023).

Default Skin:

double bun,  underboob cutout, white dress, white pantyhose, le_malin_(azur_lane), pauldrons, epaulettes, pleated dress ,cape

For V6 and onwards:: You need to replace le_malin_(azur_lane) by LeMalinDefault

Sundress :

double bun, long hair, short dress,   sleeveless, sleeveless dress,   sundress,   white dress, white_flower, white_rose,  halter dress, black camisole,  black collar, spiked collar,le_malin_(the_knight's_true_nature)_(azur_lane)

For V6 and onwards:: You need to add LeMalinSundress

Swimsuit :

double bun, long hair,  swimsuit, white bikini, le_malin_(wednesday's_retreat)_(azur_lane), halterneck, criss-cross halter, white bikini,arm scrunchie, arms behind head,black collar

For V6 and onwards:: You need to add LeMalinSwimsuit

Le Malin µ :

For V5 and V6:

ballerina, ballet dress, white pantyhose,white_footwear, wings, ballerina, double bun, long hair,tutu,white leotard,le_malin_(muse)_(azur_lane)

I suspect that this LoRA overfit it. (V5)

It had more repeat than the other skin/version because there is actually few SFW art of that skins. (V5)

16-02-2023/V6 Update: You need to add LeMalinMuse. That outfit is a bit less accurate on V6...but on the other hand it is less overffited. (no background overfitting,more flexible)

12-05-2023/V7 Update: Use this instead :

LeMalinMuse, ballerina,ballet dress, white pantyhose, double bun,  tutu, le_malin_(muse)_(azur_lane) , idol, idol_clothes, see-through,wing_hair_ornament, long sleeves,  covered_navel, star \(symbol\),

Bunny girl:

white choker, white leotard, white pantyhose, white wrist cuffs,twin braids,le_malin_(listless_lapin)_(azur_lane),fake animal ears, sleeveless, clothing cutout, rabbit ears,

(It is quite ironic that this borderline NSFW skin has way more SFW arts than Le Malin µ).

For V6 and onwards: You need to add LeMalinLapin

Model used for the example:

V7 examples: YesMix v16

V6 examples : AnythingV4.5

V5 examples : AnythingV4.5 and Pastel Mix .

That character is owned by Manjuu Games and Yostar.

modelVersions.name: V5
modelVersions.description:
Training settings:

286 images
variable repeats (15 for Le Malin µ,10 for her default/swimsuit/sundress skin and 4 for her bunny girl skin, 4 for non canon outfits) 
4 epochs
9220 steps (batch size:1)
scheduler: cosine with restart
Learning rate: 1e-4
Text encoder learning rate: 5e-5 
Unet learning rate: 1e-4 
max bucket resolution: 512 
clip skip: 2 
dim/alpha: 160 
batch size=1 
Base model: AnythingV3, this mean that this LoRA work on any model derived from that particular model like AnythingV4/4.5, Pastel Mix, AOM 1/2,etc...
